description.en: This dataset provides a headline summary of key voting statistics for GE12 at parliament level, including voter turnout, margin of victory, and rejected votes. GE12 was held on 8th March 2008.
description.bm: Dataset ini merumuskan statistik undi penting bagi PRU12 di peringkat parlimen, termasuk peratus keluar, margin kemenangan, dan undi tolak. PRU12 dilaksanakan pada 8 Mac 2008.
